"""
google_agent/source/rag_retrieval_agent.py
===============================================================================
RagRetrievalAgent — clean dynamic source-truth retrieval for AI Live Tutor.

This is a full clean replacement.

Why:
- The previous file had stacked V5/V6/V7/V8/V9 monkey patches appended together.
- That made the module fragile and caused runtime errors such as:
  "unbalanced parenthesis at position 28".
- This file keeps one clean implementation.

Contract:
- Use only real source text already present in payload/chunks/pageContexts.
- Never invent facts.
- Never use static topic-specific rules.
- PDF extracted text is truth.
- OCR/image text is helper only.
- Output rich sourceTruthPacket for downstream Concept/KG/Teaching/Vision/Board agents.
===============================================================================
"""

